{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/lloyds/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"fd620e03-de2a-5ce4-b175-1e249ef7b9ee","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e28b31d95cf0385664aafb720551021/18e3b/multi-device-top-secret.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"multi device top secret\"\n        title=\"multi device top secret\"\n        src=\"/static/1e28b31d95cf0385664aafb720551021/18e3b/multi-device-top-secret.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e28b31d95cf0385664aafb720551021/d1f95/multi-device-top-secret.jpg 500w,\n/static/1e28b31d95cf0385664aafb720551021/18e3b/multi-device-top-secret.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>As part of SapientNitro’s pitching activities with Lloyds Bank, I was asked to build a microsite to encapsulate all the information, documents, videos and event logs.</p>\n<p>From a dev perspective, the project was quite simple, but we had to be sure the website was secure and IE7 compatible, which always complicates things a little bit.</p>\n<p>The website was based on a responsive HTML5 template called <a href=\"http://themes.semicolonweb.com/html/canvas/intro.php\">Canvas</a>, which we used to quickly layout the different sections.</p>\n<p>After a few days, we decided to adapt the static website and transform it into a Wordpress theme to allow a more developer-independent content update.</p>\n<p>SapientNitro finally won the pitch ;-)</p>\n<p><i>Apologies for not displaying any media, but all the files, images, videos and documents are confidential.</i></p>","fields":{"prefix":"2015"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Lloyds Bank microsite","categories":"sapientnitro web prototype wordpress inverted","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/88da91e3eb3f3e42f60e25ea3ab57b23/47498/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lloyds/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}